track_notes: Smokemont Loop trail to W4C/WM-109.  At trail crest, follow ridgeline approx 60 yrds to summit.

From the trailhead at the bridge in Smokemont, it is 4.5 miles RT with approx 1,400 ft EG.  There is a 100 yard bushwhack to reach the summit but a faint manway is easy to follow.  Plenty of trees to get a wire up and a downed tree for op position.  Dean ~ K2JB
track_title: W4C/WM-109 Track from Trailhead in Smokemont Campgrouond.
